HB 545 Engrossed 2026 Regular Session Riser
Abstract: Provides for origination fees charged by lenders.
Present law provides that a lender may charge an origination fee that does not exceed $50
on a consumer loan or revolving loan account.
Proposed law amends that maximum fee to $75.
(Amends R.S. 9:3530(A)(1))
